The paper deals with deep learning for medical image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses domain generalization, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of data augmentation is a common technique in computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the segmentation of specific organs, which is a common topic in neural engineering (cs.NE).
